Steps.Description:
Allows mappings of fields from one data element to another. 
It can map between fields in simple data elements or fields in table data elements (loop field mapping).  Transformations can be applied to field mappings by using functions.

FX.Description: Map values depending on input. This function compares the common value with all provided cases (using the operator and the case-specific value) and returns the target value of the first matching case or the default target value.
